{
  "stem": "1603.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so at age 12, 13, there was a lot of boys who were interested in her and came up to our house and sat around there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And sometimes there was 10, 15 boys sitting there just to be around my sister and talk with her.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And nobody was really interested in me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father was a very busy businessman and under tremendous pressure.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I really don't recall a lot of things, a lot of times where he really would have been with me and with us really.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I, I, I just remember sometimes dinners and breakfasts and, and lunches.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I really don't remember that my father and I would have, what they say here in America, would have went fishing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I never went fishing with my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I could write a book about this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my grandmother and my grandfather came from a small town where they worked themself up into business.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so my-- when my father was a little boy, they-- his parents were very well doing already.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so my grandmother made it sure that my father goes into a good school and meets the right people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then he set my father up in business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Actually, my grandfather had a business called Leopold Fischl and Son.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And their business is something which, to my knowledge, is-- it's probably around in America, too, or was, but I never heard of it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Is a person who works with the large farmers and--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let's say, here the government helps the farmers, the medium farmers and large farmers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In, in, in Hungary, my father would be like working with these medium and large farming people, and let's say buying the livestock a year or two years ahead of the time before they really want to sell it.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
